=Description=

"Even before current financial crisis took hold the world was experiencing problems associated with sustainability - illustrating that if the global economy recovers we will, once again, see shortages of basic raw materials . This is especially true in the energy sector.

A number of people are attempting to address the problem of sustainability by developing and deploying renewable energy solutions using their own scientific and engineering skills.

theEnergyCrowd '''aims to collect together the experiences of engineers and developers who would otherwise be working in isolation with the intention of producing a set of practical renewable energy solutions'''."
(http://www.theenergycrowd.com/?q=node/15)


